    <body>
        <p>Once you have loaded the image, create a new Docker bridge network using the <code>docker network create </code> command. The new bridge will allow using the <code>hostname</code> to connect the event brokers in the HA group. </p>
        <p>In the example below, we have created a new Docker bridge network called <code>solace-net</code>. </p>
        <p class="Code">&gt; docker network create solace-net</p>
    </body>
